Last updated 13 May 2011.

Setting up the development environment:

For Mac OS X 10.5 and Python 2.7: 

First, install setuptools
easy_install pip
pip install numpy
pip install scipy
pip install ipython
pip install joblib

Pip does not work properly for matplotlib.
Install matplotlib from SourceForge. They had an mpkg of 1.0.1 for python
2.7.

pip install http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/static/Downloads/PyQt4/PyQt-mac-gpl-4.8.4.tar.gz
